Linux-CDROM version 0.02
=========================

This module gives you access to your CDROM (and possibly DVD) drives on
Linux. It implements most of the ioctls defined in linux/cdrom.h.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    none, but a working C compiler

